sellerCard.description: Hello, I am Abdul Haseeb. I am a WordPress Web developer.  I can develop and design any type of  website, e-commerce site or blog. If you are looking for a complete high-end, up-to-date, professional, and responsive WordPress website at affordable prices then you are in right place. I have a 4 years of experience in Web designing and development. I am known for building stunning and captivating websites for both businesses and individuals. I would love to help you with your desired website project and my goal is to provide best services to my clients.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Requirements to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
(1) Domain & Hosting with Cpanel
(2) Logo
(3) Paragraph for About Us Page
(4) List of your services with one to two paragraph about each services
(5) Email of Business, Location, Working Hours, Phone

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you build website on your own server?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can build website on my server and move it over to yours upon completion free of cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I do not have the content for the website, can we start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will add dummy content so that you would be able to replace that with your own content in future. The content will be dummy "Lorum Ipsum" and will not be relevant to any industry.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain or hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, we don't provide domain and hosting. We strongly recommend Hostgator or Bluehost for hosting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I see some samples of your work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can drop us a message to see samples of my work.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you write content for the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, you will have to provide content.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide support after completion of the job?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do provide free support according to the selected package. If you have any questions you can always inbox me even after the order is completed.
